.
.Mx
.It Fl d , Fl Fl debug
Almost enable a sandbox mode with the internal variable
.Va debug ;
the same can be achieved via
.Ql Fl S Va \&\&debug
or
.Ql Ic set Va \&\&debug .
.
.Mx
.It Fl E , Fl Fl discard-empty-messages
