.It Fl H , Fl Fl header-summary
Display a summary of
.Ic headers
for the given
.Ic file
(depending on
.Fl u ,
.Va inbox
or
.Ev MAIL ,
or as specified via
.Fl f ) .
A configurable summary view is available via the option
.Fl L .
This mode does not honour
.Va showlast .
.
.Mx
