.Mx
.It Fl T Ar """field: addr""" , Fl Fl target Ns =..
Add
.Ar addr ,
interpreted as a single addressee, to the list of receivers targeted by
.Ar field ,
for now supported are only
.Ql bcc ,
.Ql cc ,
.Ql fcc ,
and
.Ql to .
Field and body (address) are separated by a colon
.Ql \&:
and/or blank (space, tabulator) characters.
The
.Ql shquote
.Va expandaddr
flag is supported.
Via the question mark
.Ql \&?
modifier suffix the
.Fl b , c
etc. list parse mode is available, the keyword
.Ql list
is optional, e.g.,
.Ql to? ,
.Ql to?: ,
.Ql to?list
etc. are identical.
