.Mx
.Pf ( Cd mle-hist-srch-fwd ) .
.
.It Ql \ecT
Paste the snarf buffer
.Mx
.Pf ( Cd mle-paste ) .
.
.It Ql \ecU
The same as
.Ql \ecA
followed by
.Ql \ecK
.Mx
.Pf ( Cd mle-snarf-line ) .
.
.It Ql \ecV
Prompts for a Unicode character (hexadecimal number without prefix, see
.Ic vexpr )
to be inserted
